<h1><%= link_to "Home", :controller => 'main', :action => 'index' %> >> Send an e-mail to the listhost</h1>
<p><h4>Instructions</h4>
<ol>
	<li>Enter the subject and message below. All information is required.
		<br /><br /><i>Tips for completing the "Body" of the message:
			<ul style="list-style: disc inside none">
				<li>All URLs, links, and e-mail addresses will automatically be turned into clickable links</li>
				<li>Paragraph breaks and extra spaces will be respected</li>
				<li>For extra formatting, use HTML. For example, use &lt;b&gt;...&lt;&#47;b&gt; for bold text and &lt;i&gt;...&lt;&#47;i&gt; for italicized text</li>
			</ul></i>
	</li>
	<li>Messages will be delivered immediately and the operation cannot be canceled or undone. Please review your message carefully before sending (you will have a chance to preview your message in its final layout before it is sent).</li>
</ol>

</p>
<%= form_for @message, :as => :message, :url => { :action => "preview_message" }, :html => { :multipart => true } do |f| %>
<%= @message.errors.full_messages if @message.errors%>
  <p>
    <label>Subject</label><br />
    [NLRA] <%= f.text_field :subject %>
  </p>

	<p>
	    <label>Body</label><br />
	    <%= f.text_area :body, :cols => 60, :rows => 15 %>
	  </p>
	<h3>You will have the opportunity to add attachments to your e-mail on the next page</h3>
  </p>
    <%= f.submit "Preview message" %>
  </p>
<% end %>